# Monorepo MusicTrack — gitignore raíz

# Dependencias en cualquier subcarpeta
**/node_modules
**/.pnp
**/.pnp.js
**/.yarn/install-state.gz

# Builds de Next.js (frontend)
**/.next/
**/out/
**/build/

# Coverage
**/coverage/

# Variables de entorno locales
**/.env
**/.env*.local

# Vercel
**/.vercel

# Logs
**/npm-debug.log*
**/yarn-debug.log*
**/yarn-error.log*

# OS / editores
.DS_Store
*.pem
.idea/
.vscode/

# TypeScript (por si se suma)
**/*.tsbuildinfo
**/next-env.d.ts
